T1  - Advantages to Competing with Yourself: Why an Exchange Might Design Futures Contracts with Correlated Payoffs
AU  - Tashjian, Elizabeth
AU  - Weissman, Maayana
JO  - Journal of Financial Intermediation
VL  - 4
IS  - 2
SP  - 133
EP  - 157
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/04/01/
